    <detaileddescription>
<para>A pre-runtime digest.</para>
<para>These are messages from the verification engine to the runtime, although the verification engine can (and should) read them itself to avoid code and state duplication. It is erroneous for a runtime to produce these, but this is not (yet) checked. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
